02:09:16.480 --> 02:09:19.270
it never left her.

02:09:19.280 --> 02:09:21.189
She would only take a sponge bath

02:09:21.199 --> 02:09:22.870
because she was too scared to run the

02:09:22.880 --> 02:09:25.350
water. She would fill up a pot of

02:09:25.360 --> 02:09:26.950
water and take a sponge bath

02:09:26.960 --> 02:09:28.470
every time she bathed. She'd never

02:09:28.480 --> 02:09:31.030
take a full bath to fill the tub or

02:09:31.040 --> 02:09:32.709
take a shower; she'd just take a sponge

02:09:32.719 --> 02:09:34.390
and run it down her body. She did

02:09:34.400 --> 02:09:36.870
that for the rest of her life. As

02:09:36.870 --> 02:09:36.880
a generation,

02:09:36.880 --> 02:09:41.510
we don't know

02:09:41.520 --> 02:09:43.589
how bad the Great Depression

02:09:43.599 --> 02:09:45.510
was. They would eat possum. She would

02:09:45.520 --> 02:09:47.669
tell us she'd eat the possums and

02:09:47.679 --> 02:09:49.669
black crows; they would

02:09:49.679 --> 02:09:51.430
kill the black crows to make black crow

02:09:51.440 --> 02:09:54.229
pie, and they would kill and eat the cooked possum.

02:09:55.840 --> 02:09:58.390
That's how they lived.

02:09:58.400 --> 02:10:00.470
That's where she learned to dig

02:10:00.480 --> 02:10:03.189
stuff out of the ditch and survive

02:10:03.199 --> 02:10:05.589
because the Great Depression was so bad.

02:10:06.480 --> 02:10:10.299
They were very poor.

02:10:12.800 --> 02:10:14.790
She said they made dresses and clothes for

02:10:14.790 --> 02:10:14.800
the kids out of flour

02:10:14.800 --> 02:10:17.430
sacks;

02:10:22.800 --> 02:10:27.910
her parents would sew

02:10:27.910 --> 02:10:27.920
them.

02:10:27.920 --> 02:10:31.750
It was rough, and that's why the

02:10:31.760 --> 02:10:34.149
Lord says

02:10:34.159 --> 02:10:37.109
another Great Depression is coming.

02:10:37.119 --> 02:10:40.790
When I see how it affected her, I

02:10:40.790 --> 02:10:40.800
realize

02:10:40.800 --> 02:10:44.229
this generation has no clue.

02:10:44.239 --> 02:10:47.430
The things He said today shook me to

02:10:47.440 --> 02:10:49.669
even talk about it.

02:10:53.760 --> 02:10:57.589
I pray things get

02:10:57.599 --> 02:11:00.950
changed around

02:11:00.950 --> 02:11:00.960
quickly.

02:11:00.960 --> 02:11:02.870
Happy birthday, Elizabeth!

02:11:02.870 --> 02:11:02.880
It

02:11:02.880 --> 02:11:04.149
is officially her

02:11:04.159 --> 02:11:04.550
birthday.

02:11:07.119 --> 02:11:09.750
Happy birthday to you, happy birthday to

02:11:09.760 --> 02:11:14.490
you, happy birthday, dear Elizabeth.

02:11:14.500 --> 02:11:19.510
Poke

02:11:19.520 --> 02:11:21.270
salad was poisonous if it wasn't

02:11:21.280 --> 02:11:23.189
fixed right, too.

02:11:23.199 --> 02:11:24.790
Really?

02:11:24.800 --> 02:11:26.629
Wow, I didn't know. Thanks for

02:11:26.639 --> 02:11:29.750
telling us now.

02:11:29.760 --> 02:11:30.790
She isn't here to test

02:11:30.790 --> 02:11:30.800
it;

02:11:30.800 --> 02:11:32.229
I guess she fixed it right.

02:11:36.000 --> 02:11:39.270
Is that what happened to Grandpa?

02:11:39.280 --> 02:11:41.030
Oh, that's sad.

02:11:55.520 --> 02:11:57.350
We thought it

02:11:57.360 --> 02:11:59.990
was a heart attack. Did she do it on

02:12:00.000 --> 02:12:02.149
purpose?

02:12:07.599 --> 02:12:08.709
What if that's the truth?

02:12:08.719 --> 02:12:10.550
Oh, look, she says, 'My

02:12:10.550 --> 02:12:10.560
great-great-great-grandmother

02:12:10.560 --> 02:12:12.709
was Maria

02:12:12.719 --> 02:12:13.669
Woodworth-Etter.'Whoa,

02:12:13.679 --> 02:12:15.589
now that's a flex!

02:12:15.599 --> 02:12:16.149
Angel,

02:12:16.159 --> 02:12:18.229
that's cool;

02:12:19.280 --> 02:12:21.189
you have a cool bloodline.

02:12:21.189 --> 02:12:21.199
My

02:12:21.199 --> 02:12:21.750
great-great-grandpa

02:12:21.760 --> 02:12:25.886
on

02:12:25.886 --> 02:12:25.896
that

02:12:25.896 --> 02:12:26.229
side

02:12:26.239 --> 02:12:29.109
died

02:12:29.119 --> 02:12:31.669
in his 60s.

02:12:31.679 --> 02:12:33.746
And if that's the truth, what did she do?

02:12:34.639 --> 02:12:37.430
She says she is crying

02:12:37.440 --> 02:12:39.109
so hard.

02:12:40.159 --> 02:12:42.550
I figured

02:12:42.560 --> 02:12:44.950
Grandpa English went home. What happened

02:12:44.960 --> 02:12:49.669
to Grandpa? Granny did it; she didn't cook

02:12:49.679 --> 02:12:52.470
her greens.

02:12:52.480 --> 02:12:56.310
What do you do with that?

02:12:59.840 --> 02:13:02.470
A lot of people would

02:13:02.480 --> 02:13:04.229
literally freak out if they didn't have

02:13:04.239 --> 02:13:05.830
their phones. They wouldn't know what to

02:13:05.840 --> 02:13:06.790
do.

02:13:12.560 --> 02:13:14.310
I look at my phone all throughout the

02:13:14.320 --> 02:13:16.149
day and I don't even know what I'm

02:13:16.159 --> 02:13:19.589
looking at.

02:13:19.599 --> 02:13:22.390
I look at it and go, 'Why?'Sometimes the

02:13:22.400 --> 02:13:24.069
Lord asks, 'What are you looking

02:13:24.079 --> 02:13:26.390
for?'We

02:13:26.400 --> 02:13:29.350
need to

02:13:29.360 --> 02:13:32.069
put the phone down, Brandon.

02:13:34.550 --> 02:13:34.560
I'm

02:13:39.679 --> 02:13:43.109
just staring at it.

02:13:43.109 --> 02:13:43.119
I

02:13:43.119 --> 02:13:44.310
do

02:13:44.320 --> 02:13:47.669
it

02:13:47.679 --> 02:13:48.870
even through the

02:13:48.880 --> 02:13:50.470
night. I'll catch myself

02:13:50.480 --> 02:13:52.390
waking up going, 'What are you looking

02:13:52.400 --> 02:13:56.932
for? It's the

02:13:56.942 --> 02:13:57.270
night.'Well,

02:13:57.280 --> 02:13:59.552
it's just a friend of mine, I guess,

02:14:00.239 --> 02:14:02.550
just trying to check on it. I just want to

02:14:02.560 --> 02:14:08.722
make sure he's okay.

02:14:11.760 --> 02:14:14.310
The

02:14:14.320 --> 02:14:16.310
phone's still there. Oh,

02:14:16.320 --> 02:14:19.857
you have my phone.

02:14:19.867 --> 02:14:21.189
Don't mess with my

02:14:21.199 --> 02:14:21.910
friend!

02:14:21.920 --> 02:14:24.442
I was going to charge it for you.

02:14:24.452 --> 02:14:24.790
People

02:14:27.717 --> 02:14:27.727
are

02:14:29.840 --> 02:14:31.750
going to think you're

02:14:31.760 --> 02:14:32.629
serious.

02:14:33.920 --> 02:14:35.270
No, I'm not serious.

02:14:36.560 --> 02:14:37.830
Well, I do look at it all the time.

02:14:38.880 --> 02:14:40.470
They do take me too seriously.

02:14:40.480 --> 02:14:43.270
I like having fun; I'm joking.

02:14:44.880 --> 02:14:47.109
Life's good.

02:14:47.119 --> 02:14:48.870
But there is a side of me that's very

02:14:48.880 --> 02:14:50.550
serious.

02:14:53.679 --> 02:14:57.030
Life is happy.

02:14:57.040 --> 02:15:00.229
The Lord said you must remain happy in

02:15:00.239 --> 02:15:03.589
the days ahead. Enjoy life;

02:15:03.599 --> 02:15:05.189
He wants you to have it in abundance, to

02:15:05.199 --> 02:15:07.669
the full, until it overflows.

02:15:07.679 --> 02:15:10.310
We just laugh about nothing,

02:15:10.320 --> 02:15:13.189
have fun as a family,

02:15:13.189 --> 02:15:13.199
and

02:15:13.199 --> 02:15:15.533
play games.

02:15:17.040 --> 02:15:19.430
So, we love y'all. Thank you for

02:15:19.440 --> 02:15:21.109
spending time with us after the

02:15:21.119 --> 02:15:22.870
prayer.

02:15:22.880 --> 02:15:25.510
It was

02:15:25.520 --> 02:15:28.229
heavy today, y'all. I needed to laugh.

02:15:28.239 --> 02:15:30.390
There was a lot of

02:15:30.400 --> 02:15:32.470
inner surgery today and

02:15:32.480 --> 02:15:34.629
it was rough. I made it through in

02:15:34.639 --> 02:15:36.149
the Lord. It was very corrective. I

02:15:36.159 --> 02:15:39.510
told Diana it

02:15:39.510 --> 02:15:39.520
felt

02:15:39.520 --> 02:15:41.109
like I just went through a

02:15:41.119 --> 02:15:41.990
pressure cooker.

02:15:42.000 --> 02:15:43.830
It was a thunderous

02:15:43.840 --> 02:15:46.149
word—thunder,

02:15:46.159 --> 02:15:48.870
lightning, and smoke.

02:15:48.880 --> 02:15:50.870
I was like, 'Is my hair there?'Oh no,

02:15:50.880 --> 02:15:54.229
it's gone.

02:15:54.239 --> 02:15:58.069
I heard you, Lord.

02:15:58.079 --> 02:15:59.418
Uncle Fester here;

02:16:03.760 --> 02:16:10.310
I got too close to the glory.

02:16:12.400 --> 02:16:15.830
The hair's gone.

02:16:23.679 --> 02:16:26.950
You can see His glory shining on my face,

02:16:26.950 --> 02:16:26.960
on

02:16:26.960 --> 02:16:32.824
my shiny head.

02:16:40.399 --> 02:16:43.030
He gets the glory shining.

02:16:43.040 --> 02:16:45.110
It's going to be extra shiny.

02:16:45.120 --> 02:16:46.230
They're like, 'Put

02:16:46.240 --> 02:16:48.150
a little thing around your

02:16:49.990 --> 02:16:50.000
head.'Moses

02:16:52.479 --> 02:16:54.230
had

02:16:54.240 --> 02:16:55.830
white hair in the Ten Commandments; it

02:16:55.840 --> 02:16:59.589
wouldn't be that way with me.

02:16:59.599 --> 02:17:05.110
It looks like a light bulb.

02:17:10.800 --> 02:17:14.745
The glory

02:17:16.240 --> 02:17:17.830
face. Y'all aren't right!

02:17:20.719 --> 02:17:24.469
We're not. You're

02:17:24.479 --> 02:17:26.469
figuring it out.

02:17:26.479 --> 02:17:27.830
They're like, 'We're not watching you

02:17:28.870 --> 02:17:28.880
anymore,'but

02:17:30.639 --> 02:17:33.084
they're laughing.

02:17:37.120 --> 02:17:38.790
It's been

02:17:38.800 --> 02:17:42.910
a day. I'm tired now.

02:17:49.200 --> 02:17:52.389
We love you. Thank you for joining

02:17:52.399 --> 02:17:56.070
us, y'all. It means so much to us.

02:17:58.399 --> 02:18:01.030
We're just trying

02:18:01.040 --> 02:18:03.589
to be real. We

02:18:03.599 --> 02:18:06.469
love to pray, we love to seek the Lord,

02:18:06.479 --> 02:18:08.790
and we're so thankful for every single

02:18:08.800 --> 02:18:10.469
one of you that join and

02:18:10.479 --> 02:18:12.469
subscribe to our YouTube

02:18:12.479 --> 02:18:14.870
channel. It's been life-changing for

02:18:14.880 --> 02:18:17.349
us that God would choose us and use us

02:18:17.359 --> 02:18:19.750
for such a time as this. We're

02:18:19.760 --> 02:18:21.910
grateful every time you click

02:18:21.920 --> 02:18:23.830
that notification bell and do the

02:18:23.840 --> 02:18:25.750
things you do to be a part of our

02:18:25.760 --> 02:18:29.190
YouTube community. I believe that

02:18:29.200 --> 02:18:31.830
the best is yet to come. Praying in 2026

02:18:31.840 --> 02:18:34.389
and praying over this year. I

02:18:34.399 --> 02:18:35.589
believe we'll do a video

02:18:35.599 --> 02:18:38.870
tomorrow.

02:18:43.519 --> 02:18:46.790
I always sit before Him

02:18:46.790 --> 02:18:46.800
during

02:18:46.800 --> 02:18:49.750
that last special

02:18:49.750 --> 02:18:49.760
time

02:18:49.760 --> 02:18:52.790
before you cross over into the

02:18:52.800 --> 02:18:55.429
new year. It's something holy to me.

02:18:57.200 --> 02:19:00.469
I sit with Him as I get ready to

02:19:00.479 --> 02:19:02.950
take my breath into the next year and

02:19:02.960 --> 02:19:05.429
just say thank you for

02:19:05.439 --> 02:19:07.429
another year. We do

02:19:07.429 --> 02:19:07.439
it

02:19:07.439 --> 02:19:08.389
every

02:19:08.389 --> 02:19:08.399
year—making

02:19:08.399 --> 02:19:10.709
our list,

02:19:10.719 --> 02:19:12.309
writing down what we're believing God

02:19:12.319 --> 02:19:15.270
for, stretching our faith.

02:19:15.280 --> 02:19:18.709
Grab a hold

02:19:18.709 --> 02:19:18.719
of

02:19:18.719 --> 02:19:19.830
what you're believing for and

02:19:19.830 --> 02:19:19.840
say,

02:19:19.840 --> 02:19:21.589
'God, I know that You're able to do

02:19:25.110 --> 02:19:25.120
this.'We

02:19:27.679 --> 02:19:31.750
love you all again.

02:19:35.040 --> 02:19:37.509
Remember,

02:19:37.519 --> 02:19:40.309
put a smile on your face and a song in

02:19:40.319 --> 02:19:43.270
your heart. We love you, Jesus loves

02:19:43.280 --> 02:19:45.589
you, and we'll see you again soon.

02:19:45.599 --> 02:19:48.599
Bye-bye.

